---
layout: layouts/default.njk
---

<div class="banner">
  <p>
    I'm doing a 24 hour walk in aid of North Tees Hospital's Diabetes Unit.
    <a href="https://www.gofundme.com/f/lets-help-a-child-with-diabetes">Donate Here</a><span class="banner__emoji" role="img">üôè</span>
  </p>
</div>

<header class="header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="header__title">The Ramblings of a Developer.</h1>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Blog posts -->
    <div class="posts">
      {% set postslist = collections.myPosts %}

      {% for post in postslist | reverse %}
        {% set currentPost = post.data.post %}

        <article class="post">
          <h2 class="post__title">
            <a href="posts/{{ currentPost.slug.current | slug }}" class="post__link">
              {{ currentPost.title }}
            </a>
          </h2>
          {% if currentPost.excerpt %}
            <div class="post__lede">{{ currentPost.excerpt | markdownify | safe }}</div>
          {% endif %}

          <time class="postlist-date" datetime="{{ currentPost.publishedAt }}">{{ currentPost.publishedAt|readableDate }}</time>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <!-- About card -->
    <article class="card card--media card--featured">
      <div>
        <img
          class="card__image"
          src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ghm8pz5f/production/b62bb71ae29cc965c77a30ab4e32f0570ce6ff65-640x640.jpg?w=1000&h=1000&fit=max"
          alt="Jamie Bradley"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="card__title">About Me</h3>
        <p class="card__copy">
          Hey! My name is Jamie Bradley. I am the founder of Endeavour
          Digital and a Lead Front End Engineer. I live near a town called
          Middlesbrough and I enjoy playing squash.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</main>
